and I was just busy studying the sun...

619
00:39:21,225 --> 00:39:23,887
but I suppose I could do that later.

620
00:39:23,994 --> 00:39:25,894
What a coincidence.

621
00:39:25,996 --> 00:39:28,328
Maybe you can answer
a question for me.

622
00:39:28,432 --> 00:39:31,367
Oh, but- but certainly. Tell me.

623
00:39:31,469 --> 00:39:35,064
Every day the sun rises,
and every afternoon it sets.

624
00:39:35,172 --> 00:39:38,039
