666
00:42:09,527 --> 00:42:11,495
[ Master Growls ]

667
00:42:11,595 --> 00:42:15,531
- Hey! You!
- [ Gasps ] Huh?

668
00:42:15,633 --> 00:42:17,624
Yeah, I mean you.

669
00:42:17,735 --> 00:42:21,330
