670
00:42:21,438 --> 00:42:26,501
[ Whimpering, Crying ]

671
00:42:26,610 --> 00:42:30,410
So much ignorance. Unbelievable.

672
00:42:30,514 --> 00:42:33,347
- [ Crying ]
- Hey!

673
00:42:33,450 --> 00:42:36,977
- [ Sniffling ]
- You! Come back here immediately.

674
00:42:37,087 --> 00:42:39,988
We need you.

675
00:42:40,090 --> 00:42:41,853
Look through the lens.

676
00:42:41,959 --> 00:42:46,396
Okay, now watch carefully.

677
00:42:46,497 --> 00:42:50,263
